title: Aaron Rodgers!! Brady Quinn on MNF, Raiders issues, NFL news (Football 10/16)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to breakdown the incredible Monday night game between the Packers and the 49ers that featured a marvelous comeback by Aaron Rodgers with a bloody sleeve that somehow avoided overtime. Then the guys talk about the Raiders bizarre travel situation and what exactly Oakland is doing,, where Adam Thielen stands in the hierarchy of NFL wide receivers, teams they don't trust, the bizarre Ryan Tannehill injury situation and whether or not the Browns are who we think they are.
